<br>
Just a couple of hours ago i saw the Oscar nominated documentary by Michael Moore called Bowling for Columbine. I thought the documentary was great, it didn't present any real surprise cause we are practically fed with the information of violence happening in the states on the daily news. Michael Moore wasn't very objective on the issue, so if there are any pro-gunners (NRA members or wossname) that would like to dismiss him as a fool please feel free to educate me. <br>
<br>
Post any oppinion you have about gun control, respect other oppinons and for gods sake keep personal attacks to a minimum.<br>
<br>
