<br>
He cites Lockheed's plant near Littleton as a ICBM maker, yet ther contruct Rockets that launch TV Sats into Orbit.<br>
<br>
He neglects to mention that the 6yr old who found the gun was placed in a crack house, instead he lashes out on Welfare for work. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#102960><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub169.ezboard.com/bmtboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ayerishstormcaller>Ayerish Stormcaller</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Egging EW</span><br>  Posts: 330<br> <font color=#628CBC>(2/20/03 11:30:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=446.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Bowling for Columbine.</span><hr size=1> All of Moore's work is thought-provoking, but objectivity is certainly not his strong point.  He's basically the liberal version of Rush Limbaugh, but at least he's funny, and not in a nervous-laughing, 'hey-is-this-guy-crazy-or-WHAT?' kind of way.  For a guy who never finished high school, he's doing pretty well in this country for as much as he criticizes it, but I think ultimately he MEANS well.  <br>
<br>
